WeSeen : Network Operations Center System
============================================

WeSeen is web application for Network Operations Center System(NOC) to monitor and track issue from end-user.

Requirement
 - Ruby 1.9.3 or newer
 - Mysql database

Installation
 - install ruby and rails (rvm recomended) 
   curl -L https://get.rvm.io | bash -s stable --rails
   rvm install 1.9.3
   rvm use 1.9.3 --default
 - Install bundle gem 
   gem install bundle
 - Clone project from github
 - Go to root project and bundle to install dependency gem
 - Set up database.yml & application.yml
 - Create and migrate database
   bundle exec rake db:setup
 - Testing server
   bundle exec rails s

